quran[13{c,v,t}:
19,52,Wa naadainaahu min jaanibit Tooril aimani wa qarrabnaahu najiyyaa
19,53,Wa wahabnaa lahoo mir rahmatinaaa akhaahu Haaroona Nabiyyaa
19,54,Wazkur fil Kitaabi ismaa'eel; innahoo kaana saadiqal wa'di wa kaana Rasoolan Nabiyyaa
19,55,Wa kaana yaamuru ahlahoo bis Salaati waz zakaati wa kaana 'inda Rabbihee mardiyyaa
19,56,Wazkur fil Kitaabi Idrees; innahoo kaana siddeeqan Nabiyyaa
19,57,Wa rafa'naahu makaanan 'aliyyaa
19,58,Ulaaa'ikal lazeena an'amal laahu 'alaihim minan Nabiyyeena min zurriyyati Aadama wa mimman hamalnaa ma'a Noohinw wa min zurriyyati Ibraaheema wa Israaa'eela wa mimman hadainaa wajta bainaaa; izaa tutlaa 'alaihim Aayaatur Rahmaani kharroo sujjadanw wa bukiyyaa�(make sajda)
19,59,Fakhalafa mim ba'dihim khalfun adaa'us Salaata wattaba'ush shahawaati fasawfa yalqawna ghaiyaa
19,60,Illaa man taaba wa aamana wa 'amila saalihan fa ulaaa'ika yadkhuloonal jannata wa laa yuzlamoona shai'aa
19,61,Jannaati 'adninil latee wa'adar Rahmaanu ibaadahoo bilghaib; innahoo kaana wa'duhoo maatiyyaa
19,62,Laa yasma'oona feehaa laghwan illaa salaamaa; wa lahum rizquhum feehaa bukratanw wa 'ashiyyaa
19,63,Tilkal jannatul latee oorisu min 'ibaadinaa man kaana taqiyyaa
19,64,Wa maa natanazzalu illaa bi amri Rabbika lahoo maa baina aideenaa wa maa khalfanaa wa maa baina zaalik; wa maa kaana Rabbuka nasiyyaa
